and I really think a wedding
without cold salmon is...

84
00:07:45,039 --> 00:07:49,031
- I'm not allergic to salmon.
- Oh, he's not allergic to salmon.

85
00:07:49,101 --> 00:07:51,078
I don't think.
But you never know.

86
