takeout that changes your life.

129
00:10:00,301 --> 00:10:02,340
Destiny takes a hand.

130
00:10:02,410 --> 00:10:05,450
Mum, destiny is something
we've invented

131
00:10:05,553 --> 00:10:08,942
because we can't stand the fact that
everything that happens is accidental.

132
00:10:09,027 --> 00:10:12,687
Then how do you explain that you both
ordered exactly the same sandwich...

133
00:10:12,712 --> 00:10:14,118
except for the bread?

134
00:10:14,328 --> 00:10:16,187
How many people in this world...

135
00:10:16,212 --> 00:10:20,297
like lettuce and tomato without
something else, like tuna?

136
00:10:21,011 --> 00:10:25,141
Well, it wasn't a sign.
It was a coincidence.

137
00:10:25,711 --> 00:10:29,632
I was in Atlantic City with my
family, Cliff was a waiter.

138
00:10:29,777 --> 00:10:33,812
