which fingers were his and which were mine.

143
00:10:51,319 --> 00:10:55,016
- And I knew.
- What?

144
00:10:55,502 --> 00:10:56,836
You know.

145
00:10:57,718 --> 00:11:02,757
- What?
- Magic. It was magic.

146
00:11:03,876 --> 00:11:05,121
Magic.

147
00:11:05,465 --> 00:11:09,699
I knew we'd be together forever. And
that everything would be wonderful.

148
00:11:09,797 --> 00:11:12,351
